<item>
            <title>[SPARK-8572] Type coercion for ScalaUDFs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-8572</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Seems we do not do type coercion for ScalaUDFs. The following code will hit a runtime exception.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
val myUDF = udf((x: Int) =&amp;gt; x + 1)
val df = sqlContext.range(1, 10).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;i&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).select(myUDF($&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;i&quot;&lt;/span&gt;))
df.explain(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;)
df.show
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is also good to check if we do type coercion for PythonUDFs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
